caller_intent: The caller requested a quote for liability-only auto insurance.
resolution_steps: Heather confirmed the caller needed liability auto insurance.
Heather explained Alliance Insurance Services does not offer standalone liability-only policies.
Heather inquired if the caller had other policies (e.g., homeowners insurance), which they did not.
Heather informed the caller they could not assist with liability-only coverage.
knowledge_required: Understanding of Alliance Insurance Services' policy offerings
summary: A caller requested liability-only auto insurance, but the agent explained Alliance Insurance Services does not offer standalone liability policies. The caller was informed they could not be assisted with this request.
